<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero__bg">
    {% if section.settings.hero_image != blank %}
      <img src="{{ section.settings.hero_image | img_url: '1920x' }}" alt="">
    {% else %}
      <div class="page-hero__bg-placeholder"></div>
    {% endif %}
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-hero__content">
      <p class="eyebrow page-hero__eyebrow">— Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Love is the most<br><em>radioactive force</em><br>in the universe.</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="page-body">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-content">
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--white);line-height:1.6;">It started with a goodbye at an airport gate.</p>
      <p>Two people, one love, 4,000 miles of ocean between them. The kind of goodbye that hollows you out — where you can still feel the warmth of someone's hand long after they've walked away.</p>
      <p>That night, staring at the ceiling of a too-quiet apartment, the idea was born: What if there was something physical — something you could touch, hold, feel against your skin — that carried the energy of your person? Not a photo. Not a text. Something alive. Something that glowed.</p>
      <blockquote>"Radioactive" because real love doesn't fade — it radiates. It changes you at a molecular level.</blockquote>
      <p>We named it Radioactive Love because that's exactly what true connection is — an invisible, unstoppable energy that permeates everything it touches. It doesn't weaken over distance. It intensifies.</p>
      <p>Every piece we create is designed to be a conduit for that energy. The Sun and Moon bracelets aren't just matching jewelry — they're two halves of a gravitational field. Wear one, and you carry a piece of your person with you. Always.</p>
      {% if section.settings.story_image != blank %}
        <img src="{{ section.settings.story_image | img_url: '1200x' }}" alt="" class="page-section-img">
      {% endif %}
      <p>Today, Radioactive Love connects thousands of couples across every continent. From New York to London, from Tokyo to São Paulo — our pieces travel the world, carried by people who refuse to let distance define their love.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:4rem;">
      <a href="/collections/all" class="btn-primary">Shop the Collection</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}{"name":"Story Page","settings":[{"type":"image_picker","id":"hero_image","label":"Hero Image"},{"type":"image_picker","id":"story_image","label":"Body Image"}]}{% endschema %}